  "instructions": "1. Combine the romaine lettuce, cucumber, tomatoes, olives, bell peppers, and red onion in a large bowl.\n\n2. Sprinkle the salad mixture with crumbled feta cheese.\n\n3. In a small bowl, whisk together the olive oil, lemon juice, dried oregano, and ground black pepper.\n\n4. Pour the dressing over the salad and toss well to combine.\n\n5. Serve immediately or chill in the refrigerator for later.",
